== Lolnas API project

== Development

Rails Dev Tweaks is installed to significantly boost performance in development
https://github.com/wavii/rails-dev-tweaks

== Resources

Street addresses to lat/lon coordinates
http://itouchmap.com/latlong.html

JavaScript distance calculations
http://www.movable-type.co.uk/scripts/latlong.html

OpenLayers (ilmeeni kun kartta ei toimi openlayersin kotisivulla)
http://openlayers.org/

Google Maps query parameters
http://mapki.com/wiki/Google_Map_Parameters

To get bearing (not implemented yet), we could use...
http://www.rubygeocoder.com/